review.reviewBody: The cookies are insane ... best cookie around
store always forgets something or part of your order, portions are never consistent... not impressed.
Sent wrong order & items missing, portions are horrible even compared to other Tractor locations.

The food was tasty, but it's not enough. I guess the bowl is too small.
The chicken  as tasting like sometinhg  else, it had like a weird pork taste.
Everything else was good!
3 stars because It comes with some sort of ricotta chesse on top that I wasnt aware of. It does not say anywhere that they will put chesse on top.
